data.description: Welcome to 319 Gold Hill Rd, a charming brick ranch nestled on a corner lot in coveted Fort Mill, SC. This recently updated residence boasts an abundance of natural light, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. Featuring 3 bedrooms and a full bath, this home also offers a versatile bonus flex area that can be tailored to your needs, whether it be a home office, or an additional entertainment space. The modernly refreshed open kitchen is equipped with granite countertops, sleek stainless steel appliances, and ample space perfect for preparing meals with ease and entertain guests with style. Beyond the confines of this beautiful abode, you'll enjoy the perks of residing in an award-winning school district and the convenience of nearby shopping and entertainment options. With easy access to the interstate, you'll have the freedom to explore everything that the area has to offer. Take advantage of the vibrant community and immerse yourself in the nearby parks and recreational areas.
